### Configuration Details
The implementation follows the official Vercel Speed Insights documentation for React applications:

1. **Import Location**: Line 5 in `src/App.jsx`
   ```javascript
   import { SpeedInsights } from '@vercel/speed-insights/react';
   ```

2. **Component Placement**: Line 93 in `src/App.jsx`
   ```javascript
   <main className="App">
     <Analytics />
     <SpeedInsights />
     {/* Rest of the application */}
   </main>
   ```

The component is correctly placed at the top level of the application, right after the Analytics component, ensuring proper tracking of Core Web Vitals across all pages.

